snippet.title: Amber Heard REACTS To Being SENTENCED To 4 Years In Prison!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard REACTS To Being SENTENCED To 4 Years In Prison!
If you haven't heard of the drama between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, then you are surely missing out on Hollywood's most interesting story! Perhaps you heard about fans boycotting Depp's movies, and even calling him names on the internet. Well, it all relates to this story, a love story that changed overnight into a long, tumultuous court case. For a long time, the star of Pirates of the Carribean has been the antagonist in the story, with several movie fans around the world boycotting his movies. However, shocking details have recently emerged, details that could change the entire trajectory of this story.
